<h1>About This Project</h1>

<p>
  This application was developed as part of the Rails Intro Project.
</p>

<p>
  This web application allows users to browse a large library of books,
  search by title, explore authors and categories, and view detailed
  information about each book.
</p>

<h2>Project Features</h2>

<ul>
  <li>Browse over 58,000 books.</li>
  <li>View detailed information about each book.</li>
  <li>Browse books by author.</li>
  <li>Browse books by category.</li>
  <li>Search books by title.</li>
  <li>Pagination for easier navigation.</li>
  <li>Responsive Bootstrap interface.</li>
</ul>

<h2>Technologies Used</h2>

<ul>
  <li>Ruby on Rails</li>
  <li>SQLite3</li>
  <li>Bootstrap</li>
  <li>CSV Data Import</li>
</ul>